@startuml Trip Management Sequence Diagram

title Trip Management Sequence Diagram

actor ":Staff" as Staff
actor ":Renter" as Renter
participant ":Frontend" as FE
participant ":Backend" as BE
participant ":Payment Gateway" as PAYOS

note across
  **Precondition:** Booking is **CONFIRMED**.
  Deposit paid, cars assigned.
  Continues from Booking Sequence Diagram.
end note

' ── 1. Staff Confirms Pickup ──
Staff -> FE : 1. View booking (CONFIRMED)
activate FE
FE -> BE : 1.1 GET /api/staff/bookings/{id}
activate BE
BE --> FE : 1.2 Booking details
deactivate BE
FE --> Staff : 1.3 Display booking detail page
deactivate FE

Staff -> FE : 2. Click "Confirm Pickup"
activate FE
FE -> BE : 2.1 PUT /api/staff/bookings/{id}/confirm-pickup
activate BE
note right of BE
  Validate status == CONFIRMED.
  Set actualReceiveDate = now().
  CONFIRMED → **IN_PROGRESS**.
end note
BE --> FE : 2.2 Updated booking (IN_PROGRESS)
deactivate BE
FE --> Staff : 2.3 Success notification
deactivate FE

' ── 2. GPS Tracking ──
note over FE
  **GPS Tracking (client-side emulation)**
  Leaflet.js + OpenStreetMap.
  Simulated car movement every 3s.
  No backend calls.
end note

' ── 3. Staff Confirms Return ──
Staff -> FE : 3. Click "Confirm Return"
activate FE
FE -> BE : 3.1 PUT /api/staff/bookings/{id}/confirm-return
activate BE
note right of BE
  Validate status == IN_PROGRESS.
  Set actualReturnDate = now().
  Compare actual vs expected return.
end note

alt On time or early
    BE -> BE : 3.2a Set status → COMPLETED
    BE --> FE : 3.3a Booking (COMPLETED)
    deactivate BE
    FE --> Staff : 3.4a "Booking Complete" banner
    deactivate FE

else Late return — overdue
    note right of BE
      Calculate overdue charge:
      ceil(overdueHours) × hourlyRate × 1.5.
      Update totalPrice & remainingAmount.
      Keep status = IN_PROGRESS.
    end note
    BE -> PAYOS : 3.2b Create overdue payment link
    activate PAYOS
    PAYOS --> BE : 3.3b checkoutUrl
    deactivate PAYOS
    BE --> FE : 3.4b Booking (IN_PROGRESS) + overdueCharge
    deactivate BE
    FE --> Staff : 3.5b Overdue alert + pending payment
    deactivate FE

    ' ── 4. Renter Pays Overdue ──
    Renter -> FE : 4. View booking, click "Pay Now"
    activate FE
    FE -> PAYOS : 4.1 Redirect to PayOS checkout
    deactivate FE

    Renter -> PAYOS : 5. Complete overdue payment
    activate PAYOS
    PAYOS -> BE : 5.1 Webhook (orderCode, PAID)
    activate BE
    note right of BE
      OVERDUE_PAYMENT → PAID.
      All payments resolved →
      IN_PROGRESS → **COMPLETED**.
    end note
    deactivate BE
    PAYOS --> FE : 5.2 Redirect to success page
    deactivate PAYOS
    activate FE
    FE --> Renter : 5.3 Payment success
    deactivate FE
end

' ── 5. Booking Complete ──
Staff -> FE : 6. View booking
activate FE
FE -> BE : 6.1 GET /api/staff/bookings/{id}
activate BE
BE --> FE : 6.2 Booking (COMPLETED)
deactivate BE
FE --> Staff : 6.3 "Booking Complete" (no further actions)
deactivate FE

Renter -> FE : 7. View booking
activate FE
FE -> BE : 7.1 GET /api/bookings/{id}
activate BE
BE --> FE : 7.2 Booking (COMPLETED)
deactivate BE
FE --> Renter : 7.3 Booking completed, all payments resolved
deactivate FE

note across
  **Final Status: COMPLETED.**
  All payments settled. Booking lifecycle ends.
end note

@enduml
